      "description": "Three illusory duplicates appear in your space, move with you, and mimic your actions. Each time a creature hits you with an attack roll, roll a d6 for each remaining duplicate. If any d6 rolls 3 or higher, one duplicate is hit instead and destroyed. The duplicates ignore all other damage and effects. The spell ends when all three duplicates are destroyed. A creature is unaffected if it has the Blinded condition, Blindsight, or Truesight.",
